{
  "stem": "24130.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Our shul also had not a Jewish person that took care on our shul and made fire in the winter time, because we didn't have-- we had wood-- wooden stove-- stoves that used wood to make fire.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So a Jew wasn't allowed to-- a Christian wasn't allowed to work for Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the person that took care on the shul, he wasn't allowed to work either.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the shul was cold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And on Saturday we would go to shul-- the girls didn't go at all.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the men would go, and they would make it very fast because it was very cold.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the Carpathian Mountains, it was very-- we had very strong winters.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it affected, because the people couldn't get together so much.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And like I said, this Levente harassed the Jewish people with the beards.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they harassed the boys from the-- from the Kheyder.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And once I remember the Kheyder didn't have a place in our town.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everybody-- let's say, if we had two boys, so we had two weeks Kheyder in our house.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We gave them a room and that room.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I remember the Kheyder was in our house and the Levente came with one gen-- two gendarme came.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And one of my uncles was the rabbi.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they took my uncle and my-- the kids.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They gave them a book.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they took them all around the town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they were taking him to the city hall.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we knew when they going to get to the city hall with my uncle, that they're going to hit him.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So my aunt ran fast to somebody that knew the president-- the, like-- he was like the president from our shul.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was close with somebody from the gendarme.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They shouldn't hit my uncle.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
